# ACTIVAI — environment variables
#
# The AI Coach can call Google Gemini server-side. This is OPTIONAL:
# the app ships with "Demo mode" ON by default and renders fully with
# instant pre-written coach responses even when no key is present.
#
# To enable the live Gemini path:
#   1. Get a FREE key from Google AI Studio: https://aistudio.google.com
#      (no credit card required)
#   2. Copy this file to ".env.local" and paste your key below
#   3. In the AI Coach screen, toggle "Demo mode" OFF to use the live API
#
GEMINI_API_KEY=

# Optional: override the free-tier Flash model (defaults to gemini-2.5-flash).
# Verify the current free Flash model in Google AI Studio.
# GEMINI_MODEL=gemini-2.5-flash
